Notes on concept topics:
Keep concepts short. You should be able to skim them in about a minute.

= Title
What would you enter into a search engine to learn more about this idea?
For SEO, include how Open Liberty relates to this topic.

== Short description
When you scroll through a list of search results from a search engine, what would you look for?

== Section 1: Include one diagram or one code snippet
Example: A diagram comparing monolithic architecture and microservices architecture

== Section 2: Include one paragraph or one list
Example: A paragraph that explains the differences between web services and microservices.

== Section 3: One or two sentences explaining what you can do with this concept.
Example: A link to a guide that helps you create your own microservice.
